---
title: North Indian Style Coconut Chicken Breast Curry with Green Beans and Zesty Rice
description: This North Indian Style Coconut Chicken Breast Curry is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W29_UK_R3938-23_Main_3swaP_low-94d4791f.jpg
